The example I'm providing is a title known as Seishokuki. Currently it has 17 volumes however only 6 of them are available online. This manga follows a schoolgirl with a high libido thrust into a conflict between humans and an alien race that absorbs the sexual energy of women.

I'm quite interested to know if there are other manga out there similar to this one. I'll post several images from this series, I hope you all like it as much as I did.
